text: Mesobaena rhachicephala is a worm lizard species in the family Amphisbaenidae. It is endemic to Pará, Brazil. ==References== Category:Mesobaena Category:Endemic fauna of Brazil Category:Reptiles of Brazil Category:Reptiles described in 2009 Category:Taxa named by Marinus Steven Hoogmoed Category:Taxa named by Roberta Richard Pinto Category:Taxa named by Wáldima Alves Da Rocha Category:Taxa named by Emiliane G.
